# Session orchestrator

**Fresh hub / bootstrap** ‚Üí `./scripts/repos-status.sh` then `.cursor/skills/bootstrap-hub/SKILL.md` (agent asks for repos if missing).

**Start work** / `/start-work` ‚Üí load `.cursor/skills/session-orchestrator/SKILL.md`. You run `./scripts/*`.

**Workflow** / `/workflow` ‚Üí load `.cursor/skills/workflow-orchestrator/SKILL.md`. Resume from `workflow.json` phase; do not restart from chat history. **Autopilot:** brief/plan gates only; mark-ready ‚Üí code review same turn; no pause closings between inner loops.

**`/workflow status`** ‚Üí same skill; one-screen status from `workflow.json`.

**`accept brief`** / **`accept`** ‚Üí workflow gate 1 (phase `brief_review`).

**`accept plan`** ‚Üí workflow gate 2 ‚Üí `./scripts/workflow-accept-plan.sh <codename>`.

**`reopen brief`** / **`reopen plan`** ‚Üí `python3 scripts/workflow-reopen-brief.py <codename>` / `python3 scripts/workflow-reopen-plan.py <codename>`.

**End session** / `/end-session` ‚Üí load `.cursor/skills/session-end/SKILL.md`.

**Template version / upgrade hub** ‚Üí load `.cursor/skills/hub-upgrade/SKILL.md`. Run `./scripts/hub-status.sh` first; upgrade only when user says so.
